nnot be explained by models with or\nwithout a disk. However, the $L/M$ of these objects suggest that they could be\nassociated with hypercompact/ultracompact HII regions. Therefore, the low\nmethanol emission toward the high-luminosity sources can be explained by them\nhosting an HII region where methanol is absent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Oct 2022 20:20:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
