ynomial and\nnon-polynomial, in a purely algebraic way, but also to obtain coefficients from\nthe action of ladder operators also in an algebraic manner based on further\ncommutation relations between monomials of the generators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2022 08:29:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-02"}
