aying amplitude. The frequency and the decay length are\nrelated in an intuitive, but not elementary way to the filling fraction.\nDifferent states at the same filling fraction can have distinct values for\nthese parameters. Finally, we also use our scaled correlation functions to\ncalculate estimates for the magneto-roton gaps of the various states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2022 10:35:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2023 13:10:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
